<div class="how-to-invite">
    <h2>How to invite a new member</h2>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h3 class="panel-title">Sending a new invitation</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
            <p>People this message showed can invite a new menber from the <a href="{{ path('member_invitation') }}">invitation</a> page.</p>
            <ol>
                <li><p>Before you send the invitation, you have to check whether the <a href="{{ path('member_organization_index') }}">organization</a> where the new member will belong to is exist or not. If not, you have to create the organization for him/her first.</p>
                    <p><small><span class="text-muted">You don't need to fill out all of the information. Name and a few fields are only required.</span></small></p>
                </li>
                <li><p>Go to the invitation page.</p></li>
                <li><p>Enter the user name that only used in the invitation mail and email address of the person you would like to invite.</p></li>
                <li><p>Click the Send invitation button to send.</p></li>
                <li><p>If you are sending more than one invitation, you can also continue to send it to the other people.</p></li> 
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>